-## Development
-
-### 1. Environment
-
-Your machine will need:
-
-1. Node.js >=18.17.0
-2. Docker
-
-### 2. Run all dev apps
-
-  ```bash
-  # Install pnpm on your machine
-  $ npm i -g pnpm
-
-  # Install all dependencies
-  $ pnpm i
-
-  # Start the development databases
-  $ cd /compose/databases
-  $ docker compose up -d
-
-  # From the monorepo root, start the apps
-  $ pnpm dev
-  ```
